divs: sighting detailsmy dog woke me went to see cause of barking. 4 november 2011\\\0825 utc--0842 utc bright light and movement. unsure what it was. extreme bright white light with erratic jerky, circular movement & hovering approximately 45-75 degrees above horizon in southern sky. object went out of sight by moving away to nothing. news reports this am have no serious wrecks that would require a dustoff (air ambulance). residence is not on any commercial or military vector flight path. uhf amateur radios & scanner\commercial fm&am radio wouldn't function correctly. dish network had distorted signal with black&white display. i'm a trained observer; us army retired, lrrp, military mp, security professional, police work-auxiliary, ex-private pilot, and weather spotter. did not report to local pd's, because county has 2 mobile officers usually 20 miles from my location.
Summary: UHF amateur radios&scanner/Commercial FM&AM radio wouldn't function correctly. Dish network had distorted signal with black&white display. My dog woke me up with barking to the south of house and would not stop.
